title: Delicias al Natural
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Previously all veg but no longer since Nov 2012. Pleasant, traditional Antioquian breakfast and lunch spot on a quiet street in the historic center. Two blocks north from Parque Periodista. Daily changing menu, has vegan bread and pastries, arepas, burgers, local-style veggie meat dishes, coffees, soy milk, juices. Two comfortable seating areas.
